text: Kampong Speu is a province in Cambodia. The capital city is Chbar Mon. Kampong Speu in Khmer means "starfruit port". In the province is Phnom Aural, the tallest peak in Cambodia. There is also the Phnom Aural Wildlife Sanctuary and Kirirom National Park.
